be plastered on every bus bench from Santa Cruz to Cambridge.

&quot;What is REST?&quot; &quot;Simple! *SLAP*&quot; Just put that sticker over the person
asking the questions mouth. &quot;Now you can speak REST too!&quot; Easy :).

Regards,

Will Hartung
(willh@...)

